data.description:
Discover your dream home in the peaceful community of Temple, Texas with Belton ISD! This delightful and generously-sized residence offers a perfect blend of comfort, functionality, and contemporary elegance. With its convenient location near schools, parks, shopping centers, and major transportation routes. Step inside and feel immediately welcomed by the warm and inviting atmosphere of the open concept layout. Seamlessly connecting the living, dining, and kitchen areas, this design encourages both entertaining and daily living. The gourmet kitchen stands as the heart of the home, boasting ample cabinetry, a center island, and stainless steel appliances. The master suite provides a stylish and tranquil retreat. Featuring a spacious bedroom, walk-in closets, and an en-suite bathroom with a luxurious soaking tub, and dual vanity sinks! **UPDATE: FRESHLY PAINTED BATHROOMS!!!**
 This wonderful home in Sage Meadow, Temple, Texas, is more than just a property; it's an opportunity to create cherished memories with your loved ones!
